title: The Journey
author: Luvian_Nexus
pages:
#- Hello, this is one of my books (if not t he only one) I'm bringing to you this days of war and crime.

This is the story of a boy who woke up in the most unexpected place possible and ended up with having more than he could ever imagine.
#-         Chapter 1
  The Awakening
I slowly opened my eyes to realize I was in the most deserted place in our planet, not a single soul was in sight and I was the only sane man in kms.
Dunes of sand high as the sky sorounded me, scattered rests of an 
#- abandoned house were behind me and I only could get the only usable materials that were left after who knows what happened there.
It was already nightime and I was preparing myself to go into the unkown in search of my friends, they were all
#- I ever had, no family, no work, just them.
In fact they were my only real family. The sun was rising slowly on the horizon adn i started swimming with my materials and an apple i found near a tree in an oasis.
#- To Be Continued....

(Excuse any grammar mistakes I had to do this in a rush as the AFK thing would kick me out, hope you enjoy it! ) 

Love, Agus(Luvian)
#- 